      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Inspection of blow-by gas reduction system"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. PCV hose, breather tube Inspect"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "500_3.0_jpn_11292019_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "500_3.0_jpn_11292020_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Inspect the PCV hose (A) and breather tube (B) for cracks, damage, disconnections, blockages, or looseness."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. PCV valve Inspection"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "500_3.0_jpn_11292021_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Check that the PCV valve makes a seating sound when the hose (A) between the PCV valve and intake manifold is lightly crushed during idling.",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000503",
          "label": "Replace PCV valve",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "If there is no seating sound Replace PCV valve and re-inspect.",
          "refs": [
            {
              "id": "R000503",
              "label": "Replace PCV valve",
              "resolved": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "If there is no seating sound Replace PCV valve and re-inspect.",
